# Professional Loan Eligibility Prediction System

This project is a **Machine Learning / Banking Logic-based Loan Eligibility Prediction System** built with Streamlit.

## Features

- Applicant login via Email + OTP (demo mode)
- Bank Admin login with pre-set email
- Realistic banking scoring:
  - Debt-to-Income Ratio (DTI)
  - Loan-to-Value Ratio (LTV)
  - Income weighting (log scale)
  - Credit history, property area, loan term adjustments
- Admin Dashboard: tables, charts, CSV download
- CSV logging of all enquiries

## Deployment

1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
